featured_reviews.review_id:
Time of Namaz ul Juma is 1:30pm .
It's one of the big mosque in this area .
Wheelchair accessible entrance gate but you can access with it .
More than five hundred people can perform the salat at a time .
Mosque is newly constructed and well infrastructured .
It's has big parking space on road only for salat .
Separate ablution house .
Good place for peace .
